# Duty chip time display

- Time ranges in palette duty chips must always stay on a single line (e.g. `14:00-14:40`, not wrapped at the hyphen).
- Use `white-space: nowrap` and `font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums` on `.duty-chip small`.
- Do not revert to `white-space: normal` on time text unless the user explicitly asks.
